txt.en: Many threats still lurk in the Noman-lands.\n\nYou should defeat foes in the Noman-lands.
You have cleared out enough threats to the Host of the West for one day, but there will always be more work to do.
Destroy monsters found in the Noman-lands.
Blighted wildlife, foul creatures from the Dead Marshes, and Orcs still roam the Noman-lands. You feel it would be best to continue the work of culling these threats from the area.
